{
  "id": 2739,
  "name": "Belo'ren, Child of Al'ar",
  "description": "One of the last clutch of Al'ar, Belo'ren was raised for the purpose of protecting the Isle of Quel'Danas. In the aftermath of the Voidspire, Belo'ren has been irradiated by Void. Confused and freshly hatched, the phoenix is focused on its sole task: Keep any invaders from reaching the Sunwell.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "body_text": "Belo'ren guards the Sunwell with both Light and Void magic. His [Voidlight Convergence] infuses players with either Light or Void, protecting them from one while leaving them vulnerable to the other.\r\n\r\nWhen his health is depleted, Belo'ren retreats into an ashen egg and begins to cast [Rebirth]. Players must damage Belo'ren to diminish his [Immortal Flame] before he is reborn anew.",
      "spell": null,
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Damage Dealers",
          "body_text": "$bullet; [Light Feather] reduces incoming Holy damage. [Void Feather] reduces incoming Shadow damage.\r\n$bullet; Damage from [Light Dive] and [Void Dive] is split evenly between all players hit.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Healers",
          "body_text": "$bullet; [Light Feather] reduces incoming Holy damage. [Void Feather] reduces incoming Shadow damage.\r\n$bullet; [Light Burn] and [Void Burn] absorb significant healing and inflict damage over time until fully healed.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Tanks",
          "body_text": "$bullet; [Light Feather] reduces incoming Holy damage. [Void Feather] reduces incoming Shadow damage.\r\n$bullet; Failing to hit a player with [Guardian's Edict] empowers Belo'ren, significantly increasing his damage.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
